Class EventHandlerAttribute

The EventHandlerAttribute is used to handle arbitrary events for the Node Editor. 'priority' can additionally be specified. A priority over or equals hundred will be called AFTER the GUI Method Signature must be [ Return: Void; Params: NodeEditorInputInfo, EventType ]
